metadata.name: אוהד - Leque Voa sobre o Viaduto
metadata.description:
That is the first picture,
of a series of spontaneous and
atemporal meta-Culture.

Among all the kinds of Art plus moving,
Bodies going beyond,
As the wind blowing
over my head, I am dancing all around.

São Paulo, July of 2022
Viaduto Nove de Julho
